'''馬德琳·麦卡恩失蹤事件'''是2007年5月3日晚發生在[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]][[阿爾加維|阿爾加維]]{{link-en|普拉亞·達·盧什|Praia da Luz}}的一件女童失踪案。女童名叫'''馬德琳·貝絲·麥卡恩'''（{{lang-en|Madeleine Beth McCann}}，{{bd|2003年|5月12日}}），當時只有三歲。此案是現代歷史上最知名的人口失蹤案之一，麥卡恩的行蹤至今不明。<ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/1902515/Master-of-media-circus-for-Madeleine-McCann.html "Master of media circus for Madeleine McCann"], ''The Daily Telegraph'', 24 April 2008.</ref>

瑪德琳當時正在葡萄牙與父母凱特（Kate）和格里·麥卡恩（Gerry McCann）及其他家庭成員一起度假。其父母在晚上八時半離開在公寓一樓睡覺的她和其孿生胞弟前往{{convert|50|m}}外的餐廳就餐。<ref>以下連結有顯示公寓及餐廳之間的直接距離：[http://uk.reuters.com/article/2007/05/04/uk-portugal-girl-idUKL0439120620070504 "Kidnapping concern for missing girl in Portugal"], Reuters, 4 May 2007; Kate McCann, ''Madeleine'', Bantam Press, 2011 (hardback edition), p. 54.</ref> 晚上10點時其母發現瑪德琳失蹤，葡萄牙警方最初認為這是一起誘拐綁架案，但後來誤讀英國發出的DNA分析報告而誤判瑪德琳已經死亡。<ref>Esther Addley, [http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2012/apr/27/madeleine-mccann-hope "Madeleine McCann: hope and persistence rewarded"], ''The Guardian'', 27 April 2012: "It was, the [Portuguese] attorney general found, largely due to a catastrophic misinterpretation of the evidence collected by ... [Leicestershire police] that the Portuguese team came to suspect the McCanns in the disappearance."</ref> 2007年9月其父母被懷疑謀殺了女孩，但次年7月得以澄清，當月葡萄牙司法部長宣佈結案。<ref>James Sturcke and agencies, [http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2008/jul/21/madeleinemccann.internationalcrime "McCanns and Murat formally cleared in case of missing Madeleine"], ''The Guardian'', 21 July 2008.</ref>

在2011年5月[[蘇格蘭場|蘇格蘭場]]在英國內政大臣的要求下宣佈展開[[格蘭赫行動|格蘭赫行動]]（Operation Grange）介入調查前，麥卡恩夫婦一直僱用私人偵探進行調查。2013年10月葡萄牙警方也開始重新調查此案，當月蘇格蘭場發佈了嫌犯的電子合成照片，其中一張照片顯示一名男子攜帶著瑪德琳在事發當晚走向沙灘。此外包括[[J·K·羅琳|J·K·羅琳]]在內的社會各界人士給此案提供了懸賞金。<ref name=Laville14Oct2013>Sandra Laville, [http://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2013/oct/14/british-detectives-efits-madeleine-mccann-suspect "British detectives release efits of Madeleine McCann suspect"], ''The Guardian'', 14 October 2013.</ref>

這樁失蹤案引發了廣泛的國際關注。麥卡恩夫婦在瑪德琳失蹤後被錯誤地認為涉嫌謀殺而遭到來自[[推特|推特]]和各種小報的人身攻擊，<ref>For Diana comparison, Nicola Rehling, "'Touching Everyone': Media Identifications, Imagined Communities and New Media Technologies in the Case of Madeleine McCann," in Ruth Parkin-Gounelas (ed.), ''The Psychology and Politics of the Collective: Groups, Crowds and Mass Identifications'', Routledge 2012, p. [http://books.google.com/books?hl=en&lr=&id=jBzHwqMfdegC&oi=fnd&pg=PA152 152ff].For Twitter, Eilis O'Hanlon, [http://www.independent.ie/opinion/analysis/eilis-ohanlon-the-sad-rise-of-cyber-courts-full-of-twittering-bullies-26848113.html "Eilis O'Hanlon: The sad rise of cyber courts full of Twittering bullies"], ''Sunday Independent'' (Ireland), 29 April 2012.Also see Brian Cathcart, [http://www.newstatesman.com/law-and-reform/2008/10/madeleine-mccann-daily-british "The Real McCann Scandal"], ''New Statesman'', 23 October 2008.</ref> 2008年他們收到了賠償金及來自英國出版商[[北殼集團|北殼集團]]的道歉，這也導致要求限制新聞輿論的聲音增強。<ref>[http://www.levesoninquiry.org.uk/hearing/2011-11-23pm/ "Wednesday 23 November 2011; afternoon session"], Kate and Gerry McCann's testimony, Leveson Inquiry, from 08:40 mins; [http://www.levesoninquiry.org.uk/evidence/?witness=gerry-mccann Transcript and witness statement of Gerry McCann] and [http://www.levesoninquiry.org.uk/evidence/?witness=kate-mccann Kate McCann], Leveson Inquiry.</ref><ref>James Robinson, [http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2011/nov/23/leveson-inquiry-mccann-testimony-tabloids "Leveson inquiry: McCanns deliver damning two-hour testimony"], ''The Guardian'', 23 November 2011.</ref>2020年，德國檢察官假定馬德琳·麥卡恩死亡，並且表示一名43歲德國籍連環性侵犯「克里斯坦·B（Christian B）」涉有重嫌。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-52916137|title=Madeleine McCann assumed dead - German prosecutors|date=2020-06-04}}</ref>

==背景==
===人物===
====瑪德琳麥卡恩====
[[File:EU_location_POR.png|thumb]]，北部和西部臨近[[西班牙|西班牙]],南部臨近[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]]]]
瑪德琳出生於2003年5月12日,住在[[英國|英國]]的[[萊斯特|萊斯特]]{{link-en|洛斯雷|Rothley}}。她擁有着金髮碧眼，在側小腿有小形棕色胎記，因患有[[虹膜異色症|虹膜異色症]]，導致雙眼呈現藍色和綠色，並在右眼的綠色[[虹膜|虹膜]]上有一條獨特的深色条纹<ref name=“PJ”>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070824192128/http://www.policiajudiciaria.pt/htm/Ingles/missing_person/madeleine.htm|title=missing child}}, PJ. </ref>。2009年，英國警方為麥卡恩夫婦提供了一張瑪德琳6歲的{{link-en|年代進展圖|age progression}}，並在2012年提供了9歲的<ref> Haroon Siddique, {{cite web|url= https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/may/01/madeleine-mccann-picture|title= Madeleine McCann's parents release picture of how she might look now}}, The Guardian, 1 May 2009.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/9226178/Madeleine-McCann-Police-release-new-age-progression-image.html|title=Madeleine McCann: Police release new 'age progression' image}} , The Daily Telegraph, April 2012.</ref>。

====凱特和格里麥卡恩====
瑪德琳的父母均為羅馬天主教徒。母親凱特麥卡恩先後就讀於安菲爾德的諸聖學校和埃弗頓谷的聖母高中，並於 1992 年畢業於[[鄧迪大學|鄧迪大學]]，獲得醫學學位。她曾短暫地進入了婦產科，然後再進入了麻醉科，最後是全科{{sfn|McCann|2011|pp=7–10, 18–19}}。

父親格里麥卡恩於1968年出生於[[格拉斯哥|格拉斯哥]]，曾就讀於{{link-en|荷里路德中學|Holyrood Secondary School}}，並在1989年從[[格拉斯哥大學|格拉斯哥大學]]畢業完成生理學/運動科學學士學位。1992 年，他獲得了醫學資格，並於 2002 年獲得了來自格拉斯哥的醫學博士學位。2005 年以來，他一直是{{link-en|萊斯特格倫菲爾德醫院|Glenfield Hospital}}的心臟病專家顧問<ref>[http://www2.le.ac.uk/departments/cardiovascular-sciences/people/mccann "Dr Gerry McCann"], University of Leicester. Also see {{harvnb|Spence|2007|p=1168}}.</ref> 。麥卡恩夫婦於 1993 年在格拉斯哥相識，並於 1998 年結婚。有三個孩子，分別是2003年出生瑪德琳和2005年出生的龍鳳胎西恩(Sean)和艾米莉(Emelie) {{sfn|McCann|2011|pp=17, 26, 37}}。

====塔帕斯七人====
麥卡恩夫婦在案發當時在與七個朋友和八個孩子一起度假，其中包括瑪德琳和瑪德琳弟妹{{sfn|McCann|2011|p=42}}。晚上20:30九位大人一般都在度假村的[[塔帕斯|塔帕斯]]餐廳一起用餐，因此媒體將這七個大人為“塔帕斯七人” <ref name=TapasSeven>Angela Balakrishnan, [https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2008/apr/10/madeleinemccann.ukcrime "Key players in the McCann case"], ''The Guardian'', 2008-04-10; [http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/7331034.stm "Who are the McCann tapas seven?"], BBC News, 2008-10-16.</ref>。塔帕斯七人中包括菲奧娜和大衛佩恩斯，他們都是醫生，他們家庭中前往的成員包括他們的兩個孩子以及菲奧娜的母親黛安韋伯斯特。麥卡恩與佩恩斯相識多年。凱特在2000年在萊斯特綜合醫院的重症監護室工作時認識菲奧娜{{sfn|McCann|2011|p=20}}。陪同他們的是佩恩斯最初介紹給麥卡恩家族的兩對夫婦，營銷經理簡·坦納 (Jane Tanner) 和她的合夥人、醫生拉塞爾·奧布萊恩 (Russell O'Brien)，他們都帶著兩個孩子去度假，以及另一位醫生馬修·奧德菲爾德 (Matthew Oldfield)與他的妻子、律師雷切爾·奧爾德菲爾德和他們的女兒在一起。多年來，格里、拉塞爾和馬修一直在一起工作{{sfn|McCann|2011|p=42}}<ref name=TapasSeven/>。根據簡.唐納的報告，她曾看到一名男子從45分鐘前報導瑪德琳度假村攜帶孩子帶走失踪成為案件的最討論方面之一{{sfn|McCann|2011|p=76}}。

=== 案发地点 ===
2007年4月28日，麦卡恩一家抵达葡萄牙[[阿尔加维大区|阿尔加维大区]]{{tsl|en|Praia da Luz|普拉亚达卢兹}}村，开启为期七个夜晚的春假。普拉亚达卢兹村人口1000，因是英国人度假定居的热门地点，固有“小英国”之称<ref name=Bachrach2008>Judy Bachrach, [https://www.vanityfair.com/news/2008/02/mccanns200802 "Unanswered Prayers"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223093444/http://www.vanityfair.com/news/2008/02/mccanns200802 |date=23 December 2020 }}, ''Vanity Fair'', October 2008.</ref>。麦卡恩一家通过英国度假公司{{tsl|en|Mark Warner Ltd|马克·华纳公司}}租下{{le|阿戈斯蒂尼奥·达席尔瓦|Agostinho da Silva}}博士路5A的一间公寓，房东为利物浦的一位退休教师<ref name=Gammell8Aug2008>Caroline Gammell, [https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/madeleinemccann/2523523/Madeleine-McCann-Apartment-was-not-made-crime-scene-for-two-months.html "Madeleine McCann: Apartment was not made crime scene for two months"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180122012459/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/madeleinemccann/2523523/Madeleine-McCann-Apartment-was-not-made-crime-scene-for-two-months.html |date=22 January 2018 }}, ''The Daily Telegraph'', 8 August 2008.</ref>。

公寓位于地下层，有两间卧室，属于水边村（Waterside Village）公寓群的第五栋，地处马克华纳公司旗下海洋俱乐部（Ocean Club）度假村的附近<ref name=Balakrishnan11April2008(1)>Angela Balakrishnan, [https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2008/apr/11/madeleinemccann1 "The resort that was rocked one night in May"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301093935/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2008/apr/11/madeleinemccann1 |date=1 March 2017 }}, ''The Guardian'', 11 April 2008.</ref>。麦卡恩一家的邻居有住在5B的马修和蕾切尔·奥德菲尔德（Matthew and Rachel Oldfield）、5D的珍·坦纳和罗素·奥布莱恩（Jane Tanner and Russell O'Brien），以及同栋一楼的佩恩斯和黛安·韦伯斯特（Paynes and Dianne Webster）{{sfn|McCann|2011|p=45}}。由于处在阿戈斯蒂尼奥·达席尔瓦博士路和{{le|弗朗西斯科·让蒂尔|Francisco Gentil|弗朗西斯科·让蒂尔·马丁斯博士}}路的交界处，外人可以从两边进入5A<ref>DCI Andy Redwood, [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OZ8jmdWlB8Y ''Crimewatch''] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216060651/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OZ8jmdWlB8Y |date=16 February 2016 }}, BBC, 14 October 2013, from 00:20:02.</ref>。从客厅后方的滑动玻璃露台门可俯瞰海洋俱乐部的游泳池、网球场、小吃餐厅和酒吧，也可以前往公用的让蒂尔·马丁斯博士路，来到通往5A栋阳台及客厅的小门及台阶。5A栋的前门则位于达席尔瓦博士路海洋俱乐部街区的对面<ref name=Balakrishnan11April2008(2)/><ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=InJLmyakzeE "Searching for Madeleine"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150327100323/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=InJLmyakzeE&feature=youtu.be |date=27 March 2015 }}, ''Dispatches'', Channel 4, 18 October 2007, 00:15:21.</ref>。

麦凯恩的两个孩子睡靠近的前门的卧室，房门一直被麦凯恩一家锁住。卧室有一个带窗帘的齐腰高窗户，窗帘后是一个在外面的百叶窗，由窗内的绳索控制。整个假期里，麦凯恩一直拉上百叶窗和窗帘。从窗户可以俯瞰狭窄的人行道和居民停车场，后者有一堵矮墙和道路分开<ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=InJLmyakzeE "Searching for Madeleine"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150327100323/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=InJLmyakzeE&feature=youtu.be |date=27 March 2015 }}, ''Dispatches'', 00:06:25.</ref>。马德琳睡在靠近卧室房门、窗户对面的单人床，同时双胞胎的旅行婴儿床放在房间中间，窗下还有一张单人床<ref name=Balakrishnan11April2008(2)/>。

== 案发过程 ==
=== 白天：麦卡恩家庭活动 ===
5月3日星期四是麦卡恩一家假期的倒数第二。吃完早餐，玛德琳问：“昨天晚上（哥哥）和我哭的时候，你们怎么没有过来？”玛德琳失踪后，父母怀疑这句话意味着晚上有人进了他们的房间。另外，母亲注意到马德琳睡衣上衣有一个很大的棕色污点{{sfn|McCann|2011|pp=62–64}}。

上午，父母带两个孩子在度假村的儿童俱乐部（Kids' Club）玩，中午在公寓吃午饭，之后到泳池玩水<ref name=Balakrishnan11April2008(2)>Angela Balakrishnan, [https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2008/apr/11/madeleinemccann "What happened on the day Madeleine disappeared?"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170213090939/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2008/apr/11/madeleinemccann |date=13 February 2017 }}, ''The Guardian'', 11 April 2008.</ref>。下午2点29分，凯特给玛德琳拍了最后一张公开的照片，当时玛德琳与父亲及两岁的妹妹坐在泳池边<ref>Giles Tremlett, [https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2007/may/25/ukcrime.madeleinemccann1 "McCanns release last picture of Madeleine before she vanished"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220205254/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2007/may/25/ukcrime.madeleinemccann1 |date=20 December 2016 }}, ''The Guardian'', 25 May 2007.{{br}}
For 2:29 pm: Laura Roberts, [https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/madeleinemccann/8506277/Madeleine-McCann-Kate-McCann-fears-outfit-may-have-led-to-kidnap.html "Madeleine McCann: Kate McCann fears outfit may have led to kidnap"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181011121606/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/madeleinemccann/8506277/Madeleine-McCann-Kate-McCann-fears-outfit-may-have-led-to-kidnap.html |date=11 October 2018 }}, ''The Daily Telegraph'', 11 May 2011.</ref>。之后孩子回到儿童俱乐部，当晚6点和母亲回到5A，父亲则去上网球课<ref name=Balakrishnan11April2008(2)/>。晚上7点左右，父母哄孩子们上床睡觉，玛德琳穿着[[玛莎百货|玛莎百货]]的粉白相间{{tsl|en|Eeyore|屹耳}}短袖睡衣，旁边有一条[[慰藉物|安抚巾]]，还有毛绒玩具抱抱猫（Cuddle Cat）{{sfn|McCann|2011|pp=67, 69}}。

=== 晚上8点30分：小吃餐厅 ===
晚上8点30分，夫妇俩离开5A，陪朋友到海洋俱乐部泳池边的露天小吃餐厅吃饭<ref name=McCann2011pp69-70/>。5A与餐厅{{tsl|en|as the crow flies|直线距离}}55米（180英尺），但去餐厅要走过一条公用道路，来到海洋俱乐部度假村的大门，之后再穿过度假村到泳池另一边，全程82米（295英尺）<ref name=distance>For "50 metres (yards)", [http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-portugal-girl-idUKL0439120620070504 "Kidnapping concern for missing girl in Portugal"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806215136/https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-portugal-girl-idUKL0439120620070504 |date=6 August 2020 }}, Reuters, 4 May 2007.{{br}}
For 60 yards as the crow flies, and a 90-yard walk, "less than a minute's walk away", {{harvnb|Summers & Swan|2014|p=12}}. Ninety yards would take a minute to walk at a speed of around three miles per hour.</ref>。从公寓楼楼顶可以看到小吃餐厅，但看不到大门。由于露台的门只能从里面锁，麦卡恩一直拉上门，但没有锁，窗帘也拉开，方便他们随时回去观察孩子的动态。露台台阶顶部有一个儿童安全锁，底部有一扇矮门，矮门通向大街<ref name=McCann2011pp69-70/>。

{{anchor|note}}度假村员工在泳池接待区的留言簿留下一条字条，要求在麦卡恩一家假期最后四晚的晚上8点半给夫妇俩及朋友预订能俯瞰公寓的那张桌子，方便家长们监督在公寓里睡觉的孩子。案发后，凯特推测绑匪看过那张字条{{sfn|McCann|2011|pp=56, 325}}。大约每隔半个小时，麦卡恩夫妇和朋友会回去看孩子。当晚9点05分左右，盖瑞第一次回5A看孩子。据他回忆，当时孩子睡得很沉很安稳，但原本虚掩的房间全开了，于是他把门关上，之后回到餐厅<ref name=McCann2011pp69-70>{{harvnb|McCann|2011|pp=69–70}}.</ref>。

=== 晚上9点15分：坦纳的发现{{anchor|Tanner sighting}}===
小吃餐厅七人组的简·坦纳注意到一名带着孩子的男子，她的发现成为早期调查的关键。当时是晚上9点，坦纳离开餐厅，回去看完女儿，途径让蒂尔·马丁斯博士路时碰到加里，后者9点05分回去查看完，正在回餐厅的路上。加里停下了和一位英国的度假旅客聊天<ref name=ODonnell14Dec2007/>，但两个人都不记得见过坦纳。由于博士路比较窄，葡萄牙警方听完坦纳的证词觉得十分困惑，开始指责坦纳编造了目击事件<ref name=Smith16Dec2007/>。

据坦纳向警方表示，大约9点15分，她注意眼前有一名男子正带着一个小朋友路过让蒂尔·马丁斯路和达席尔瓦路交界的十字路口。男子离玛德琳的睡房不远，一直往5A公寓前门反方向朝东走去<ref>"Reconstruction of Tanner sighting", "Madeleine was here", ''Cutting Edge'', Channel 4 (UK), 10 May 2009, 4/5, [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=na4aBr5PTYY&t=2m34s 00:02:34] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170406075241/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=na4aBr5PTYY&t=2m34s |date=6 April 2017 }}.</ref>。在最初的调查中，男子步行方向成为关键系哪所，因为他正朝33岁英裔葡萄牙男子[[#Murat|罗伯特·穆拉特]]的家走去，而他的家就在5A附近，所以穆拉特成为本案第一嫌疑人{{sfn|Summers & Swan|2014|p=85}}{{sfn|McCann|2011|p=76}}<ref name=Gammell5Aug2008>Caroline Gammell, [https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/madeleinemccann/2503890/Madeleine-McCann-Map-shows-where-abductor-was-spotted.html "Madeleine McCann: Map 'shows where abductor was spotted'"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190121100543/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/madeleinemccann/2503890/Madeleine-McCann-Map-shows-where-abductor-was-spotted.html |date=21 January 2019 }}, ''The Daily Telegraph'', 5 August 2008.</ref>。

男子怀里抱着的孩子穿着一件浅粉色睡衣，裤腿及袖口处有花卉的图案，与玛德琳所穿的衣服类似。坦纳形容这个男子白皮肤、黑发、身高1.7米（5.7英尺）、35到40岁左右，从相貌上看似南欧人或地中海沿岸地区人。男子上身穿着一件黑色夹克，下身是一条金色（或浅褐色）的裤子，完全不是游客的打扮。凯特表示，玛德琳报告失踪后，坦纳就将这条消息告诉给葡萄牙警方，对方直到5月25日才向媒体公开了情况<ref name=McCann2011p84>{{harvnb|McCann|2011|p=84}}.</ref>。玛德琳基金会请了一位法庭画家画这名男子的素描，于2007年10月公开<ref name=McCann20110p230>{{harvnb|McCann|2011|pp=230, 273, 370}}.</ref><ref>Michelle Pauli, [https://www.theguardian.com/news/blog/2007/oct/26/imageofmadeleinesuspect?INTCMP=SRCH "Is this Madeleine McCann's abductor?"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160916103907/https://www.theguardian.com/news/blog/2007/oct/26/imageofmadeleinesuspect?INTCMP=SRCH |date=16 September 2016 }}, ''The Guardian'', 26 October 2007.{{br}}
Martin Hodgson, [https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2007/oct/26/ukcrime.madeleinemccann "McCanns release sketch of man seen near apartment"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160916095049/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2007/oct/26/ukcrime.madeleinemccann |date=16 September 2016 }}, ''The Guardian'', 26 October 2007.</ref>。

凭借这个重要的发现，调查人员确认了案发时间，但苏格兰场的人认为男子抱着的是[[红鲱鱼|红鲱鱼]]<ref name=Redwoodinterview15Oct2013/>。2013年10月，苏格兰场将坦纳看到的男子认定为一名英国度假者，当时这位度假者回海洋俱乐部的夜间托儿所接女儿回公寓<ref>Peter Walker, [https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2013/oct/14/madeleine-mccann-inquiry-suspect-sighting-false-lead "Madeleine McCann inquiry shifts as sighting found to be false lead"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160813222643/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2013/oct/14/madeleine-mccann-inquiry-suspect-sighting-false-lead |date=13 August 2016 }}, ''The Guardian'', 14 October 2013; {{harvnb|Summers & Swan|2014|p=254}}.</ref>。他们让度假者穿上跟当晚一样和类似的衣服，用坦纳所述的姿势站着，拍下他的照片。男子女儿所穿的睡衣和坦纳报告的一样。农庄行动（Operation Grange）首席警探、[[总督察|总督察]]安迪·雷德伍德（Andy Redwood）表示，他们“几乎可以确认”坦纳所见与绑架案无关<ref name=Redwoodinterview15Oct2013/><ref>DCI Andy Redwood, ''Crimewatch'', BBC, 14 October 2013, from [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OZ8jmdWlB8Y&t=21m16s 00:21:16] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170405163041/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OZ8jmdWlB8Y&t=21m16s |date=5 April 2017 }}.</ref>。

=== 晚上10点：史密斯的发现{{anchor|Smith sighting}} ===
否认坦纳的发现对确认案发时间非常重要后，调查人员把重心放在当晚另一位带着孩子的男子身上。这位男子由马丁和玛丽·史密斯2007年5月26日向葡萄牙警方报告<ref>DCI Andy Redwood, ''Crimewatch'', BBC, 14 October 2013, from [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OZ8jmdWlB8Y&t=23m27s 00:23:27] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170405163043/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OZ8jmdWlB8Y&t=23m27s |date=5 April 2017 }}.{{br}}
[http://www.independent.ie/lifestyle/madeleine-mccann-few-people-rent-apartment-5a-since-maddie-vanished-26850396.html "Madeleine McCann: Few people rent apartment 5A since Maddie vanished"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217142826/http://www.independent.ie/lifestyle/madeleine-mccann-few-people-rent-apartment-5a-since-maddie-vanished-26850396.html |date=17 February 2017 }}, ''Irish Independent'', 5 May 2012.</ref>。2013年，苏格兰场认为史密斯夫妇的发现确定了玛德琳被绑架的大概时间<ref name="Laville14Oct2013"/><ref name=SundayTimes27Oct2013/>。

晚上10点左右，史密斯夫妇在离麦卡恩公寓{{convert|500|yards|meters}}的小学街（Rua da Escola Primária）看到一名男子离开海洋俱乐部前往4月25日街（Rua 25 de Abril）和沙滩，带着一名约莫三四岁的女孩。女孩棕色头发、白皮肤，穿着浅色睡衣，光着脚，男子30岁左右，1米75到1米8（5.7英尺到7.5英尺），身材苗条，棕色短发，穿着奶油色或米色长裤<ref name=McCann2011p98>{{harvnb|McCann|2011|p=98}}.</ref><ref>"Madeleine was here", ''Cutting Edge'', Channel 4 (UK), 10 May 2009, 4/5, 00:05:55; ''Crimewatch'', BBC, 14 October 2013, from 00:23:35.</ref>。在麦卡恩夫妇的聘请下，奥克利国际（Oakley International）于2008年根据史密斯夫妇的证词生成男子的{{tsl|en|E-FIT|电脑合成影像}}，后来苏格兰场于2013年在[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]《{{tsl|en|Crimewatch|英国犯罪观察}}》上首次公开该图像<ref>Patrick Counihan, [http://www.irishcentral.com/news/Irish-couple-key-witnesses-as-British-police-launch-new-enquiry-into-Madeleine-McCann-case-227647711.html "Irish couple key witnesses as British police launch new enquiry into Madeleine McCann case"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103081741/http://www.irishcentral.com/news/Irish-couple-key-witnesses-as-British-police-launch-new-enquiry-into-Madeleine-McCann-case-227647711.html |date=3 November 2013 }}, ''Irish Central'', 14 October 2013.</ref>。

=== 晚上10点：失踪报告 ===
凯特原本要在9点30分回去看孩子，但七人组中的马修·奥德费尔德也要去旁边的5A看孩子，顺道看了凯特的孩子。马修发现麦卡恩家的儿童房房门打开，但里头没有动静传出。马修没有进房间看玛德琳在不在，也记不清房间窗户和外面的百叶窗当时有没有打开。在早期的调查中，葡萄牙警方指责奥德费尔德参与其中，因为他自愿提出帮忙看孩子，有可能通过睡房窗户将玛德琳递给其他人<ref name=Balakrishnan11April2008(2)/><ref name=McCann2011p123>{{harvnb|McCann|2011|p=123}}.</ref>。

晚上10点左右，凯特回5A检查。苏格兰场于2013年表示玛德琳可能这在这个时间点之前被人带走的<ref>BBC ''Crimewatch'', 14 October 2013, from 00:23:35.</ref>。据凯特会议，她通过公寓后面未上锁的露台门进入，发现孩子们的睡房房门打开。就在她打算关门的时候，一股强劲的气流砰的一下关上了房门，由此看到睡房窗户和百叶窗打开着。玛德琳的摇篮猫和毛巾还在床上，人倒是不见了。稍微检查完公寓，凯特急忙跑回餐厅，大喊“玛德琳丢了！有人带走了她！”<ref>{{harvnb|McCann|2011|pp=[https://books.google.com/books?id=PIT6SeWkVcAC&pg=PA72 71–73]}}; "Madeleine was here", Channel 4 ''Cutting Edge'', 10 May 2009, [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lhACS6ck-Dw 1/5] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150430042203/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lhACS6ck-Dw&app=desktop |date=30 April 2015 }}, 00:00:45.</ref>。

大约10点10分，加里派马修·奥德费尔德去度假村的接待处报警，10点30分度假村启动失踪儿童搜索机制{{sfn|McCann|2011|p=74}}，出动60名员工及游客四处找人，直至凌晨4点30分。最初大家认为玛德琳迷路了，其中一人向[[第四台_(英国)|第四台]]《{{tsl|en|Dispatches (TV programme)|新聞快遞}}》栏目表示整个卢什都可以听到搜索人员在叫玛德琳的名字<ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=InJLmyakzeE "Searching for Madeleine"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150327100323/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=InJLmyakzeE&feature=youtu.be |date=27 March 2015 }}, ''Dispatches'', Channel 4, 18 October 2007, 00:08:36; for the first search being abandoned at 4:30 am: 00:09:33.</ref>。

== 初期反应 ==
===葡萄牙警方行动===
[[國家憲兵|國家憲兵]]{{tsl|en|Guarda Nacional Republicana|共和国国民警卫队}}的两名警察从5英里（8公里）远的[[拉古什|拉古什]]赶来，晚上11点10分抵达度假村{{sfn|McCann|2011|pp=75–76}}。结束完凌晨的简要搜查，他们通报了附近[[波尔蒂芒|波尔蒂芒]]的{{tsl|en|Polícia Judiciária|司法警察}}。凯特回忆司法警察在凌晨1点刚过的时候到场<ref name="McCann 2011, 78">{{harvnb|McCann|2011|p=78}}.</ref>。根据警察所述，接警不到10分钟，他们就抵达现场<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/6984836.stm "Madeleine McCann: The evidence"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180414071846/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/6984836.stm |date=14 April 2018 }}, BBC News, 8 September 2007.</ref>。凌晨2点，警方把两条巡逻犬带到度假村，8点出动了四条[[嗅探犬|嗅探犬]]<ref>Polícia Judiciária files, cited in {{harvnb|McCann|2011|p=85}}.</ref>。他们取消了假期，将卢兹的下水道、水井、洞穴和废墟翻了个遍<ref name=Bachrach2008/><ref>"Searching for Madeleine", ''Dispatches'', Channel 4, 18 October 2007, 00:20:20.</ref>。波尔蒂芒总督察[[#Gonçalo_Amaral|贡萨洛·阿马拉尔]]担任调查总指挥<ref name=Hamilos3Oct2007/>。

众所周知，警方在案发后的“黄金时间”内犯了很多错误，[[边防机构|边防机构]]和[[水上警察|水上警察]]有好几个小时没有接到玛德琳的情况，警方也没有每户上门搜查<ref>Steven Morris, [https://www.theguardian.com/crime/article/0,,2074964,00.html#article_continue "Q&A: Madeleine McCann"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220314171256/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2007/may/08/ukcrime.madeleinemccann#article_continue |date=14 March 2022 }}, ''The Guardian'', 8 May 2007.</ref><ref name=Summers2014p237>{{harvnb|Summers & Swan|2014|pp=237–328}}.</ref>。凯特表示警方到了第二天早上10点才设{{tsl|en|roadblock|路障}}<ref name=McCann2011p98/>。警方没有要求提供案发当晚离开卢兹的车辆监控画面，也没有要求提供西班牙边境地带拉各斯及[[圣安东尼奥雷阿尔城|圣安东尼奥雷阿尔城]]车辆画面。负责道路监控的公司Euroscut表示警方没有找他们要信息<ref>Richard Edwards and Fiona Govan, [https://web.archive.org/web/20070521053106/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/main.jhtml?xml=%2Fnews%2F2007%2F05%2F19%2Fwmaddy19.xml "Maddy police ignored vital CCTV"], ''The Daily Telegraph'' 19 May 2007.</ref>。[[国际刑警组织|国际刑警组织]]花了五天时间，才行发布全球{{tsl|en|Interpol notice|国际刑警组织告示|失踪人口警告}}<ref name=McCann2011p98/>。另外，警方也没有采访案发当时在度假村的所有，度假者也是后来才跟英国警方说没有联系过他们<ref name=Summers2014p237/>。

[[犯罪现场|犯罪现场]]未收到保护。葡萄牙警方采集了玛德琳睡房的样本，把样本送去三个法医实验室验证。据司法警察总督察奥莱加里奥·德·索萨（Olegário de Sousa）表示，2007年6月1日，警方找到一位“陌生人”的DNA，但房间关门前有大约20人进入5A公寓<ref name=BBC17June2007>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/6761669.stm "Madeleine evidence 'may be lost'"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070718021829/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/6761669.stm |date=18 July 2007 }}, BBC News, 17 June 2007.</ref><ref name=Smith16Dec2007/>。凯特表示，凌晨3点有位警官在儿童房的门口贴上的胶带，之后就离开了，没有保护好现场<ref name="McCann 2011, 78"/>。根据司警2008年发布的文件，案发一个月后，5A一直处于闲置状态，之后于2007年8月被封锁，方便进行后续的调查搜证<ref name=Gammell8Aug2008/><ref>Richard Edwards, [https://web.archive.org/web/20080226053520/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/main.jhtml?xml=%2Fnews%2F2007%2F06%2F01%2Fwmaddy101.xml "The 15 key blunders"], ''The Daily Telegraph'', 2 June 2007.</ref>。公寓外面也出现了类似的情况，一大群人聚焦在5A公寓的前门，包括儿童睡房窗户的旁边（这里极有可能是绑匪进入或离开的地方），踩踏了证据{{sfn|Collins|2008|pp=xxxi–xxxii}}。一位警察在没有戴手套或穿防护衣的情况下在窗户外面的百叶窗扫指纹<ref name=Smith16Dec2007>{{cite news |last1=Smith |first1=David James |title=Kate and Gerry McCann: Beyond the smears |url=http://www.thesundaytimes.co.uk/sto/news/world_news/article76941.ece |work=The Sunday Times |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406192351/http://www.thesundaytimes.co.uk/sto/news/world_news/article76941.ece |archive-date=6 April 2016|url-status=dead}}</ref>。
{{Wide image|Praia da Luz, Algarve, Portugal, February 2015 (cropped).jpg|800px|Panoramic view of Praia da Luz, February 2015}}

===英国警方行动===
玛德琳家乡的{{tsl|en|Leicestershire Police|莱斯特郡警察}}在同意的情况下派出特遣队，负责协调英方的行动。行动队伍由{{tsl|en|Chief Constable|地区警察局局长}}{{tsl|en|Matt Baggott|马特·巴戈特}}率领，与葡萄牙方的调查同期进行<ref>{{harvnb|Summers & Swan|2014|pp=48–49}}; [http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/northern_ireland/8196354.stm "Profile: Matt Baggott"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170303053001/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/northern_ireland/8196354.stm |date=3 March 2017 }}, BBC News, 11 August 2009.</ref>。双方组成了一个代表战术协调小组（或称{{tsl|en|Gold–silver–bronze command structure|金银铜指挥结构|金色小组}}），由莱斯特郡警察、[[嚴重及有組織犯罪調查局|嚴重及有組織犯罪調查局]]、{{tsl|en|Child Exploitation and Online Protection Centre|儿童剥削和网络保护中心}}及{{tsl|en|National Police Improvement Agency|国家警察改进署}}的代表组成。司法警察明面上给英方提供了一个工作房间，暗地里不满他们前来。英方习惯把资料输入到[[內政部大型重要查詢系統|內政部大型重要查詢系統]]，葡方则用箱子搜集资料。另外，葡方没有英方那样的自治权，一般要等候[[裁判官|裁判官]]做决定，工作效率大大降低。在{{tsl|en|Anthony Summers|安东尼·桑默斯}}和{{tsl|en|Robbyn Swan|罗宾·斯旺}}的《寻找玛德琳》（''Looking for Madeleine''，2014）一书中，时任儿童剥削和网络保护中心主任{{tsl|en|Jim Gamble|吉姆·甘布尔}}表示葡萄牙觉得他们屈尊于英国这样的“殖民大国”{{sfn|Summers & Swan|2014|pp=48–49}}。

===媒体与公关===
{{further|#小报与社交媒体|#玛德琳基金会}}
[[File:McCann_Tributes1.jpg|thumb]]
2010年，葡萄牙司法警察的一名官员承认他们在“[[媒体马戏团|媒体马戏团]]”的影响下，从一开始就怀疑麦卡恩一家<ref name=Govan12Jan2010/>。2008年，加里向《[[名利场_(杂志)|名利场]]》杂志表示，他曾决定“推销”玛德琳，让她一直受到公众的关注。结果，在当地警方的极为不满、认为媒体关注会有反作用之下，一群[[公共关系|公共关系]]顾问来到卢玆<ref name=Bachrach2008/>。英国公关机构{{tsl|en|Bell Pottinger|贝尔波特廷格}}的亚历克斯·伍尔法（Alex Woolfall）在案发前十天一直代表马克·华纳公司跟媒体打交道，之后英国政府也派了新闻官，情况前所未见<ref>"Madeleine McCann: A Global Obsession", Channel 5 (UK), 18 November 2014, [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=84zqo6jSprQ&t=15m48s 00:15:48] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170405143810/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=84zqo6jSprQ&t=15m48s |date=5 April 2017 }}.</ref>。

在《[[每日镜报|每日镜报]]》当记者的新闻官雪莉·多德（Sheree Dodd）率先抵达，之后{{tsl|en|Central Office of Information|中央信息办公室}}的克拉伦斯·米切尔（Clarence Mitchell）主任抵达。英方召回米切尔后，麦卡恩一家又在猎头的帮助下聘请了贾斯婷·麦吉尼斯（Justine McGuinness）。贾斯婷离开后，由首相[[约翰·梅杰|约翰·梅杰]]前私人秘书查尔斯·莱文顿（Charles Lewington）持有的汉诺威通讯（Hanover Communications）进场<ref>Ben Dowell, [https://www.theguardian.com/media/2007/sep/13/marketingandpr.crime "McCanns' PR steps down"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815054032/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2007/sep/13/marketingandpr.crime |date=15 August 2016 }}, ''The Guardian'', 13 September 2007.{{br}}
Hannah Marriott, [http://www.prweek.com/article/768338/hanover-calls-time-mccanns "Hanover calls time on McCanns"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170304114105/http://www.prweek.com/article/768338/hanover-calls-time-mccanns |date=4 March 2017 }}, ''PR Week'', 21 November 2007; David Quainton, [http://www.prweek.com/article/739282/mccanns-fine-tuning-pr "McCanns still fine-tuning PR"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170304035958/http://www.prweek.com/article/739282/mccanns-fine-tuning-pr |date=4 March 2017 }}, ''PR Week'', 19 September 2007.</ref><ref name=Tremlett17Sep2007>Giles Tremlett, [https://www.theguardian.com/media/2007/sep/17/mondaymediasection13 "With prejudice"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815052845/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2007/sep/17/mondaymediasection13 |date=15 August 2016 }}, ''The Guardian'', 17 September 2007.</ref>。2007年9月，{{tsl|en|Everest Windows|圣母峰之窗}}布赖恩·肯尼迪（Brian Kennedy）提出支付米切尔的薪水，方便她回来。随后米切尔辞去公职，全职投入麦卡恩一家的工作，由玛德琳基金会支付薪水<ref name=Telegraph24April2008>[https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/1902515/Master-of-media-circus-for-Madeleine-McCann.html "Master of media circus for Madeleine McCann"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190504094425/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/1902515/Master-of-media-circus-for-Madeleine-McCann.html |date=4 May 2019 }}, ''The Daily Telegraph'', 24 April 2008.</ref><ref>{{harvnb|McCann|2011|pp=148, 268}}.{{br}}
Cole Morton, [https://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/profiles/clarence-mitchell-i-am-a-decent-human-being-if-i-can-help-them-i-will-1634738.html "Clarence Mitchell: 'I am a decent human being. If I can help them, I will'"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170625144553/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/profiles/clarence-mitchell-i-am-a-decent-human-being-if-i-can-help-them-i-will-1634738.html |date=25 June 2017 }}, ''The Independent on Sunday'', 1 March 2009.</ref>。

2007年5月15日，麦卡恩一家创立[[#Madeleine's_Fund|玛德琳基金会：不遗余力有限公司]]，用以筹集资金，提高大家对事件的关注。基金会网站上线两天就获得5800万次点击<ref>"Madeleine McCann: A Global Obsession", Channel 5 (UK), 18 November 2014, [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=84zqo6jSprQ&t=20m58s 00:20:58] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170405143817/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=84zqo6jSprQ&t=20m58s |date=5 April 2017 }}.</ref>。5月和6月，玛德琳夫妇的公关团队安排了几项活动，维持媒体对案件的关注，包括前往葡萄牙[[花地玛|花地玛]]<ref name=Bachrach2008/>、荷兰、德国、西班牙<ref name=Tremlett28May2007>Giles Tremlett and Brendan de Beer, [https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2007/may/28/ukcrime.gilestremlett "Parents of Madeleine to visit Pope in bid to spread hunt across Europe"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170304045905/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2007/may/28/ukcrime.gilestremlett |date=4 March 2017 }}, ''The Guardian'', 28 May 2007.</ref>和摩洛哥<ref>{{harvnb|McCann|2011|pp=178ff}}; Fiona Govan, [https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/1554329/Smiles-as-children-greet-McCanns-in-Morocco.html "Smiles as children greet McCanns in Morocco"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181011115216/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/1554329/Smiles-as-children-greet-McCanns-in-Morocco.html |date=11 October 2018 }}, ''The Daily Telegraph'', 12 June 2007.</ref>。2007年5月30日，在记者的陪同下，夫妇俩乘坐{{tsl|en|Philip Green|菲利普·格林}}爵士的[[里爾噴射機|里爾噴射機]]飞到罗马，在{{tsl|en|Archbishop of Westminster|威斯敏斯特大主教}}的安排下接见教宗[[本笃十六世|本笃十六世]]<ref name=Tremlett28May2007/>。次月，世界各地300座城市放飞了玛德琳的气球<ref>[https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/06/22/AR2007062201613_pf.html "Balloons Soar for Missing British Girl"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305034714/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/06/22/AR2007062201613_pf.html |date=5 March 2017 }}, Associated Press, 22 June 2007.</ref>。

据{{tsl|en|Matthew Parris|马修·帕里斯}}表示，到6月初，记者们开始担忧专业的公关活动影响到采访<ref>India Knight, [https://web.archive.org/web/20170305034602/http://www.thesundaytimes.co.uk/sto/news/Features/Focus/article65793.ece "Lay off the McCanns"], ''The Times'', 3 June 2007.{{br}}
Kirsty Wark, [http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/programmes/newsnight/6956676.stm "Madeleine and the media"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170307130935/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/programmes/newsnight/6956676.stm |date=7 March 2017 }}, BBC News, 21 August 2007.{{br}}
Janice Turner, [http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/opinion/columnists/janiceturner/article2050773.ece "Face it: we need the McCanns to be guilty"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170304195414/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/opinion/columnists/janiceturner/article2050773.ece |date=4 March 2017 }}, ''The Times'', 15 September 2007.{pb}
Matthew Paris, interviewed for "Madeleine McCann: A Global Obsession", Channel 5 (UK), 18 November 2014, [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=84zqo6jSprQ&t=19m7s 00:19:07] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170405143815/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=84zqo6jSprQ&t=19m7s |date=5 April 2017 }}.</ref>。若以玛德琳事件为头版，一份英国报纸最多可以卖3万份<ref name=Bachrach2008/>。2007年5月28日，玛德琳登上[[人物_(杂志)|人物杂志]]封面{{sfn|Rehling|2012|p=[https://books.google.com/books?hl=en&id=jBzHwqMfdegC&oi=fnd&pg=PA153 153]}}，之后在英国各大小报的头版上出现了几乎六个月，甚至[[天空新闻台|天空新闻台]]的菜单选项也为玛德琳开辟了专区<ref name=Bachrach2008/><ref name=Freedland12Sept2007>Jonathan Freedland, [https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2007/sep/12/comment.ukcrime "Madeleine: a grimly compelling story that will end badly for us all"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216062755/https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2007/sep/12/comment.ukcrime |date=16 February 2017 }}, ''The Guardian'', 12 September 2007.</ref>。2007年5月到2008年7月间，葡萄牙小报《{{tsl|en|Correio da Manhã|晨邮报}}》共发布玛德琳的文章384篇<ref name=Machado2012p52>{{harvnb|Machado|Prainsack|2016|pp=52–53}}.</ref>。到2008年6月，在[[YouTube|YouTube]]上搜索玛德琳会出现3680条视频及700百万条贴文<ref name=Kennedy2010>{{harvnb|Kennedy|2010|pp=225, 227}}.</ref>。

== 葡萄牙方调查 ==
=== 头号嫌疑人 ===
{{further|#诽谤行为}}
玛德琳失踪12天后，34岁的英国葡萄牙裔置业顾问罗伯特·穆拉特（Robert Murat）成为案件的首位{{tsl|en|arguido|嫌疑人}}<ref name=Tremlett15May2007/><ref>[https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2008/may/01/madeleinemccann "Mild-mannered father who became first one accused"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301094413/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2008/may/01/madeleinemccann |date=1 March 2017 }}, Press Association, 1 May 2008.{{br}}
[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/7925401.stm "Murat addresses Cambridge Union"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141213171234/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/7925401.stm |date=13 December 2014 }}, BBC News, 5 March 2009.{{br}}
[http://www.cam.ac.uk/news/robert-murat-holds-cambridge-union-spellbound-in-tabloids-debate "Robert Murat holds Cambridge Union spellbound in tabloids debate"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202224951/http://www.cam.ac.uk/news/robert-murat-holds-cambridge-union-spellbound-in-tabloids-debate |date=2 December 2013 }}, University of Cambridge, 6 March 2009.</ref>。穆拉特生于[[西伦敦|西伦敦]][[汉斯史密斯|汉斯史密斯]]，住在母亲的“莉莲娜之家”（''Casa Liliana''），该处距5A公寓150码（137米），就位于[[#Tanner_sighting|坦纳目击男子]]所走的方向<ref name=Tremlett15May2007/>。《[[星期日镜报|星期日镜报]]》一位记者跟警察说穆拉特一直在问案件的情况后，警方将他列为嫌疑人。有一段时间，穆拉特是与司法警察签约的官方口译员。穆拉特说自己之所以帮忙，是因为在英国女儿也跟玛德琳一样大<ref name=Smith9Sept2007/><ref name=BBC21July2008>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/7507545.stm "Profile: Robert Murat"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222154548/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/7507545.stm |date=22 December 2016 }}, BBC News, 21 July 2008.</ref>。

小吃餐厅七人组中的菲欧娜·佩恩、拉塞尔·奥布莱恩和蕾切尔·奥德费尔德表示案发后不久看到穆拉特在5A公寓外，当时公寓外还有海洋俱乐部的一位保姆和两位英国度假者。考虑到穆拉特的住所临近5A，他的出现并不奇怪，但是他说自己和母亲整晚都呆在家里<ref>{{harvnb|McCann|2011|pp=134–136}}; {{harvnb|Summers & Swan|2014|p=89}}; Haroon Siddique, [https://www.theguardian.com/crime/article/0,,2125738,00.html "McCann friends confront Madeleine suspect"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220314171250/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2007/jul/13/ukcrime.world |date=14 March 2022 }}, ''The Guardian'', 13 July 2007.</ref><ref name=Rayner31Dec2007>Gordon Rayner, [https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/1574250/Madeleine-witnesses-cast-doubt-on-Murats-alibi.html "Madeleine witnesses cast doubt on Murat's alibi"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180703132136/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/1574250/Madeleine-witnesses-cast-doubt-on-Murats-alibi.html |date=3 July 2018 }}, ''The Daily Telegraph'', 31 December 2007.</ref>。然而，麦卡恩家的身边人仍对穆拉特持怀疑态度：其中一位支持麦卡恩一家的人告诉BBC记者理查德·比尔顿（Richard Bilton），说可以提供案件的任何最新进展，前提是比尔顿的报道需要包括新闻界对穆拉特的看法<ref>Richard Bilton, "Madeleine McCann: 10 Years On", ''Panorama'', BBC, 3 May 2017, 00:29:09.</ref>。从2007年5月15日开始，警方开始搜查穆拉特的家，排空了游泳池的水，检查了他的汽车、电脑、手机及监控录像，利用金属探测器与嗅探犬搜查了他的花园，询问了他两个手下<ref name=Tremlett15May2007>Giles Tremlett, [https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2007/may/15/ukcrime.gilestremlett "Madeleine disappearance: Briton's villa searched and three questioned by police"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170224054850/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2007/may/15/ukcrime.gilestremlett |date=24 February 2017 }}, ''The Guardian'', 15 May 2007.</ref><ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/6664271.stm "Russian denies links to Madeleine"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131025024345/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/6664271.stm |date=25 October 2013 }}, BBC News, 17 May 2007.{{br}}
[http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/6932584.stm "New Madeleine search draws blank"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071017084114/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/6932584.stm |date=17 October 2007 }}, BBC News, 6 August 2007.</ref>。2008年3月，其中一位助理放火烧了穆拉特的车子，并在人行道上用红漆写上“Fala”（说话）一词<ref>{{harvnb|Summers & Swan|2014|p=89}}; [https://www.standard.co.uk/news/murat-friend-quizzed-over-madeleine-finds-car-torched-and-the-word-speak-scrawled-beside-it-7294259.html "Murat friend quizzed over Madeleine finds car torched—and the word 'speak' scrawled beside it"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190308081856/https://www.standard.co.uk/news/murat-friend-quizzed-over-madeleine-finds-car-torched-and-the-word-speak-scrawled-beside-it-7294259.html |date=8 March 2019 }}, ''London Evening Standard'', 21 March 2008.</ref>。由于穆拉特及其朋友与失踪事件没有联系，警方于2008年7月21日结案时解除了他的嫌疑<ref name=Govan21July2008/>。2008年4月，穆拉特发起[[诽谤|诽谤]]官司达成庭外和解，其本人获得60万欧元的赔偿金；《[[观察家报|观察家报]]》表示赔偿金是英国单一诽谤官司的最大庭外和解金。穆拉特的好友各获得10万欧元赔偿<ref name=Townsend13April2008/>。2014年7月格兰赫行动期间，穆拉特的其中一位好友以目击者身份受审，审问者是苏格兰场委托的司法警察<ref name=Beer1July2014/>。同年12月，穆拉特与妻子及其他八人受审，审问者同样是苏格兰场的代表<ref name=Beer10December2014/>。2017年，穆拉特母亲作为当晚5A附近可疑事件的目击者发声。据她向英国广播公司表示，当晚她驾车路过5A公寓，发现一位身穿梅色上衣、举止可疑的年轻女子就在门外，之后便将相关情报告诉给警察。另外，她还看到一辆棕色的小型出租汽车在单行道上逆行，飞速驶向公寓方向<ref>Rozina Sabur, [https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/05/03/madeleine-mccann-investigation-key-eye-witness-says-saw-young/ "Key eyewitness says she saw young woman acting 'suspiciously' on night Madeleine McCann disappeared"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171230191448/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/05/03/madeleine-mccann-investigation-key-eye-witness-says-saw-young/ |date=30 December 2017 }}, ''The Daily Telegraph'', 3 May 2017.</ref>。

=== 目击者证词 ===
在目擊者給葡萄牙司法警察的描述中，他們描述了在馬德琳·麥卡恩失蹤前幾天和當天在5A公寓附近行為怪異的男子。蘇格蘭場開始相信這些人可能是在為[[拐賣兒童|綁架]]或{{link-en|入室盜竊|Burglary}}進行[[偵察|偵察]]。2007年1月至5月期間，入室盜竊案增加了四倍，其中包括失蹤前十七天內麥肯斯街區的兩起入室盜竊案，當中竊賊多數通過窗戶進入<ref name=Redwoodinterview15Oct2013>[https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-24528530 "Madeleine McCann: Police reveal 'pre-planned abduction' theory"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190101175903/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-24528530 |date=1 January 2019 }}, BBC News, 15 October 2013.</ref><ref name="Redwood 14 Oct, 2013 00:24:38"/> 。

